lead_paragraph: Barcelona coach Luis Enrique will wave his wand over the 'Chosen Ones' -- Lionel Messi, Luis Suarez and Neymar -- to make sure they weave their magic at Arsenal in the Champions League last-16, first leg on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Barca Ready to Weave Their Magic at Arsenal-Luis Enrique
